# Implementation: L-capstone Typed Repository Layer with CI Gate

Real stack: `drizzle-orm@0.45.2` + `better-sqlite3@12.11.1`, real (in-process) SQLite engine — no mocks, no stubbed ORM. The repository functions execute actual parameterized SQL against a live `:memory:` SQLite instance via the `better-sqlite3` native driver.

